OL,3,CWales Women head coach signs two-year
OL,4,Ccontract extension
OL,6,FCymru Women head coach Rhian Wilkinson
OL,7,Fhas signed a new two-year contract
OL,8,Fextension with the Football
OL,9,FAssociation of Wales (FAW).
OL,11,FThe deal will see Wilkinson remain in
OL,12,Fcharge throughout the 2027 UEFA
OL,13,FWomen's Nations League campaign and
OL,14,Fthe qualification campaign for UEFA
OL,15,FWomen's EURO 2029.
OL,17,FWilkinson was appointed in February
OL,18,F2024 and led Cymru to their first ever
OL,19,Fmajor women's tournament within her
OL,20,Ffirst year in charge.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
