PN,46702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779477073
OL,3,CWales Women head coach signs two-year
OL,4,Ccontract extension
OL,6,FAfter topping their qualifying group,
OL,7,FCymru secured a historic place at UEFA
OL,8,FWomen's EURO 2025 by beating the
OL,9,FRepublic of Ireland in Dublin in front
OL,10,Fof more than 25,000 fans at the Aviva
OL,11,FStadium. The team later faced the
OL,12,FNetherlands, France and England in
OL,13,FSwitzerland.
OL,15,FHowever, fans were ultimately
OL,16,Fdisappointed as Wilkinson's side faced
OL,17,Fheavy defeats in all three group
OL,18,Fmatches in Switzerland.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
