PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779477073
OL,3,CWales Women head coach signs two-year
OL,4,Ccontract extension
OL,6,FThe extension follows a strong start
OL,7,Fto Cymru's FIFA Women's World Cup 2027
OL,8,Fqualifying campaign, with the side
OL,9,Fcurrently sitting second in Group B1
OL,10,Fon goal difference.
OL,12,FWilkinson said she was "incredibly
OL,13,Fproud and privileged" to continue as
OL,14,FCymru head coach.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@UO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
