PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779477073
OL,3,CWales Women head coach signs two-year
OL,4,Ccontract extension
OL,6,FShe added: "I'm very excited to take
OL,7,Fthis team further on its journey. We
OL,8,Fhave a special group of players that
OL,9,Fdeserve to be in major tournaments, as
OL,10,Fwell as future stars that will be at a
OL,11,Fkey moment in their development over
OL,12,Fthe next few years.
OL,14,F"I'm excited for the Red Wall to see
OL,15,Fthe team develop even further over the
OL,16,Fnext few years and I would like to
OL,17,Fthank the FAW for giving me the
OL,18,Fopportunity to continue my work."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
