PN,46705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779477073
OL,3,CWales Women head coach signs two-year
OL,4,Ccontract extension
OL,6,FThe FAW's Chief Football Officer, Dr.
OL,7,FDavid Adams said: "Rhian's work has
OL,8,Fdelivered success for our National
OL,9,FTeam in recent years and her role,
OL,10,Falong with other Head Coaches across
OL,11,Fthe National Team pathway, will work
OL,12,Fto ensure successful transition of
OL,13,Fyouth players into the Women's
OL,14,FNational Team across the next 2-4 year
OL,15,Fcycle."
OL,26,@oD@SOUwD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
