PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779477073
OL,3,CWales Women head coach signs two-year
OL,4,Ccontract extension
OL,6,FNoel Mooney, the FAW's Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, also expressed his delight
OL,8,Fat the news. He said: "After the
OL,9,Fsuccess in recent years, we now look
OL,10,Fforward to seeing how Rhian and the
OL,11,Fteam develop further as we aim to
OL,12,Freach more major tournaments and grow
OL,13,Fthe Women's and Girls' game in Wales."
